			description: [
				"Tom's Simple Storage is a vanilla-style Minecraft mod that provides sophisticated inventory management without complex setup requirements. "
				""
				"To connect Storage Blocks (like chests) that are near each other, you can use an Inventory Connector. This item is placed between blocks, and it connects any Storage touching it."
				""
				"Inventory Cable Connectors serve as the interface points between your cables and storage blocks. These connectors must be placed directly against the storage block you want to connect, then linked back to your leading network using Inventory Cables."
